		<hr size="1">Ok will try to lend all the help i can here...<BR>1.  I like the LDoN camp in BB simply for the undead. Also at 610 adventure points you can get the group form of the pally temp spell.<BR>2. Stuns are my main agro getting line of spells.  My taunt is maxed and i still can have some trouble keeping agro in a raid.  So i would say use your stuns to gain agro more than anything else.<BR>3. Dont forget to get your str up too along with sta.  As far as wis goes, i am not really sure..i usually never have trouble running lom with a KEI<BR>4. I have all my skills high except for 1hb.  I maxed all the 2h skills just in case a weap with mad dmg/dly and is 2hb i can use it.</P><P>Now again, i am by far not the smartest paladin in the game, just thought i would add what i could.</P><P>Zyeer Oneblade<BR>59 paladin   <br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
